item.title: I cant log in into moparscape!
item.dc:creator: @T3h_Hate T3h Hate
item.description:
@T3h_Hate wrote:

Go to the adverts to search for a server to play on. The default 127.0.0.1 won’t work for you.
Then whenyou have found the server you want to play on. Go to the option ‘file’ then click on
new server. This is where you put the ip. Then go to ‘file’ again and click on new port. Add the port
here. If a server advert has 43594 this is what some people mean as default port which you
don’t have to change because that is the port you start with when you start the client.
